        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 8 at 5:01PM CDT by NWS Dodge City KS</headline>
        <description>At 501 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 10
miles west of Trego Center, moving east at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts of 50 to 55 mph and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Trego Center.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
